Package: LWFBrook90R
Title: Run the LWF-Brook90 hydrological model inside R
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: c(
        person("Paul", "Schmidt-Walter", email = "paul.schmidt-walter@nw-fva.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Volodymyr", "Trotsiuk", , "vtrotsiuk@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
        )
Description: Run the LWF-BROOK90 hydrological model inside R. The central
    function creates the input from model control options, parameters, soil and
    climate data, runs the LWF-BROOK90 hydrological model and returns the created output files. 
    Additionally, submodels for defining vegetation dynamics and pedotransfer functions 
    for deriving soil hydraulic parameters are provided.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    data.table (>= 1.10.4),
    vegperiod (>= 0.2.1),
    foreach,
    doSNOW,
	snow
